text: Lainingthou () is a divine title often used by male deities in Meitei mythology and religion. The term may also mean "Sovereign God". There are many gods who use this title. * Lainingthou Khoriphaba * Lainingthou Koubru * Lainingthou Nongpok Ningthou * Lainingthou Pishatao * Lainingthou Sanamahi ==Related pages== * Lairembi ==References== Category:Asian mythology
title: Lainingthou
